snippet.title: Best VGM 2063 - Tekken 7 - Kazumi's Theme
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2160 - https://youtu.be/YmaHBaNxWt0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade / PS4 / XB1 / PC
Tekken 7 (2016)
Kazumi's Theme
Akitaka Tohyama, Taku Inoue, Rio Hamamoto, Nobuyoshi Sano & Keiichi Okabe
